 King’s College, Lagos  Director and Principal of Kings College, Lagos, Mr. Andrew Agada, also challenged the graduands to make a positive change in whatever field they find themselves, noting that the students were primed to behold the world as a platform for limitless possibilities.
 
“Given your exposure to enduring values and axiomatic principles at King’s College, you are ready to nurture your innate abilities to adulthood, when you will impact the nation and indeed humanity’s growth and development.” You should, therefore, beware that the world looks up to you to provide that coveted leadership that changes the society for good.”  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .